rameter by the microwave field and gives rise to a\npeak in the temperature dependence of the harmonic-signal intensity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Dec 2003 13:50:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
